Top Guns Realty on Lake Conroe

data.description: This two-story home in Conroe, located on the east side of town, offers a spacious and comfortable living space. With three bedrooms and three full baths, the property provides ample accommodation. The kitchen features granite countertops, complemented by plenty of cabinets for storage. A detached two-car garage comes with a 25'X26' bonus room (Dad Pad) above, adding versatility to the property.  Situated on a generous 6-acre lot, the property includes a barn and a storage building, enhancing its utility. The wooded areas surrounding the home contribute to a sense of privacy, creating a serene and secluded atmosphere. The rural setting adds to the charm and potential of the property, making it an ideal retreat for those seeking a peaceful and expansive living environment with various possibilities.
